div.div:
Lessen dependency on Space; create lower-level Database wrapper/container.
Often we are moving around Space objects ONLY to get the db (Queryable) or space.id (deprecate key) i.e., HasId. Create low-level definition of DB in @dxos/echo.
1. move low-level defs out of sdk/*
2. types shoudl not depend on sdk (e.g., see plugin-inbox/types)
3. refine the following:
isSpace
getSpace => getDb
useQuery => Queryable
